        <h1>Grilled cheese sandwich</h1>

        <img src="../grilled cheese.jpeg" alt="a photgraph of a grilled cheese sandwich">

        <h2>Description</h2>

        <p>
            A grilled cheese sandwich is a classic comfort food. It can be served with
            ketchup or by itself. A great side dish otion is tomato soup.

        
        </p>

        <h2>Ingredients</h2>

        <ul>
            <li>2 Slices of bread(I use white bread)</li>
            <li>2 slices of processed cheese</li>
            <li>Butter</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Steps</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>spray cooking spray into a pan and heat pan to mediuum heat</li>
            <li>butter the outside of both peices of bread</li>
            <li>place cheese slices in between your bread(butter side out)</li>
            <li>place sandwich into pan and cook until the bread hasd a golden crust and cheese is melted</li>
            <li>remove from heat, rest for a minute then slice in half</li>
            <li>serve with ketchup or soup</li>
        </ol>
